Interface Dispatcher

  • All Superinterfaces:

    public interface Dispatcher
extends CommandCallable

      • registerCommand

        void registerCommand(CommandCallable callable,
                     String... alias)
        Register a command with this dispatcher.
        Parameters:
        callable - the command executor
        alias - a list of aliases, where the first alias is the primary name

      • getCommands

        Set<CommandMapping> getCommands()
        Get a list of commands. Each command, regardless of how many aliases it may have, will only appear once in the returned set.

        The returned collection cannot be modified.

        Returns:
        a list of registrations

      • getPrimaryAliases

        Collection<String> getPrimaryAliases()
        Get a list of primary aliases.

        The returned collection cannot be modified.

        Returns:
        a list of aliases

      • getAliases

        Collection<String> getAliases()
        Get a list of all the command aliases, which includes the primary alias.

        A command may have more than one alias assigned to it. The returned collection cannot be modified.

        Returns:
        a list of aliases

      • get

        @Nullable
CommandMapping get(String alias)
        Get the CommandCallable associated with an alias. Returns null if no command is named by the given alias.
        Parameters:
        alias - the alias
        Returns:
        the command mapping (null if not found)
